    "\"All of our projects generally have international cooperation partners.",
    "[they] naturally have to grow over a longer period of time\" (DE7).",
    "This means that connections have to be made and nurtured now for future AI development, suggesting that \"only cooperative approaches will be able to survive in competition with international players\" (DE8).",
